tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE real_estate_assets (
  asset_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  location TEXT,
  asset_type TEXT,
  num_bedrooms INT,
  num_bathrooms INT
);

CREATE TABLE Location (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    address VARCHAR(255),
    city VARCHAR(100),
    state VARCHAR(50),
    country VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE AssetSpecs (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    asset_type VARCHAR(100),
    area_sqft INT,
    bedrooms INT,
    bathrooms INT,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE real_estate_assets (
    asset_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    location VARCHAR(255),
    asset_type VARCHAR(50),
    size_sqft INT,
    build_year INT,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE asset_owners (
    owner_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    asset_id INT,
    owner_name VARCHAR(100),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE real_estate_assets (
   id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   asset_name VARCHAR(255),
   location VARCHAR(255),
   specifications TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE asset_types (
   id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   type_name VARCHAR(255),
   description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE asset_owners (
   id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   owner_name VARCHAR(255),
   contact_info VARCHAR(255),
   property_id INT
)

CREATE TABLE property_photos (
   id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   property_id INT,
   photo_url VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE property_reviews (
   id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   property_id INT,
   review TEXT
)
